{"word":"G4301 - προλαμβάνω - prolambánō - prol-am-ban'-o - Come aforehand","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">προλαμβάνω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">prolambánō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">prol-am-ban'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Come aforehand</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - முந்திக்கொள்"},{"paragraph":"1. to take before"},{"paragraph":"2. to anticipate, to forestall"},{"paragraph":"3. to take one by forestalling"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4253 - πρό - pró - pro/4253\">G4253</a> and <a href=\"#/G2983 - λαμβάνω - lambánō - lam-ban'-o/2983\">G2983</a>; to <i>take in advance</i>, that is, (literally) <i>eat before</i> others have an opportunity; (figuratively) to <i>anticipate</i>, <i>surprise:</i> - come aforehand, overtake, take before.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1949/1949\">G1949</a>, <a href=\"#/G2638/2638\">G2638</a>, <a href=\"#/G2983/2983\">G2983</a>, <a href=\"#/G3335/3335\">G3335</a>, <a href=\"#/G3336/3336\">G3336</a>, <a href=\"#/G353/353\">G353</a>, <a href=\"#/G354/354\">G354</a>, <a href=\"#/G3880/3880\">G3880</a>, <a href=\"#/G423/423\">G423</a>, <a href=\"#/G4301/4301\">G4301</a>, <a href=\"#/G4355/4355\">G4355</a>, <a href=\"#/G4356/4356\">G4356</a>, <a href=\"#/G5274/5274\">G5274</a>"}]}